Steve Ihnat https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Ihnat 0 Stefan Ihnat (August 7, 1934 – May 12, 1972) was a Slovak-born American actor and director. He immigrated to Canada when he was five years old, and later became a United States citizen. Stefan_Ihnat ( August_7_,_1934 – May_12_,_1972 ) was a_Slovak-born_American_actor_and_director .
